@startuml
title UC-05: School Supplies Donation (Activity)
left to right direction

|Donor|
start
:Log in to Donor Portal;
:Define Grant Criteria\n(Low Income, School Age, Region X);
:Allocate Budget ($10,000);

|SCP Governance|
:Validate Grant Criteria against Policies;
if (Criteria Approved?) then (no)
  :Reject & Request Amendment;
  stop
else (yes)
  :Approve Program;
endif

|SCP Core (Education & Econ)|
:Query Person Registry;
:Filter by:
- Age: 5-16
- School Enrollment: Active
- Household Income: < Poverty Line;
:Rank by Need Score;
:Select Top 500 Beneficiaries;

|Field Operations|
:Generate Distribution Task List;

|Field Agent|
:Receive Task on Mobile App;
:Visit Household;
:Verify Student Identity (QR/Biometric);
:Hand over Supplies;
:Mark Task as Complete;

|SCP Core (Education & Econ)|
:Update Beneficiary History;
:Upload Proof of Delivery;

|Donor|
:View Real-time Impact Report;
:Receive Audit Trail;
stop

@enduml
